==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: nutty
<hw>nut"ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Abounding
in nuts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having a flavor like that of nuts; <as>as,
<ex>nutty</ex> wine</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Crazy; insane; loony; batty; nuts.</def>
<mark>[slang]</mark> ⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nux vomica</ent>⟦br⟧
